#!/usr/bin/env bash
set -euo pipefail

cat <<'EOF'
Outpost CAC Helpers
-------------------

Primary command:
  cac-check
    Run CAC readiness checks and diagnostics

Common commands:
  scan
    Monitor smart card reader and card events

  reader-list
    List detected smart card readers

  nss-modules
    List NSS PKCS#11 modules used by Firefox

Useful manual commands:
  trust list
    Inspect the system trust store (includes DoD anchors)
EOF
